#===============================================================
#
#  System Host Blocker (Version 0.0.3 iOS Version)
#  A lightweight and constantly updated host blocker available for free on GitHub.
#
#  Last updated 11/4/16
#
#  Most hosts were found from scratch by me. If youâ€™d like to contribute, please try the GitHub page! Thanks!
#  Hosts were added out of alphabetical order.
#
#  Submit contributions to:
#  https://github.com/nathanaccidentally/SystemHostBlocker/issues
#
#  Created by Nathan Goodwin (nathanaccidentally)
#
#  You will need root permissions to edit host files on all operating systems.
#  Please do NOT remove anything already in your host file as it may break your connection permenantly.

