# Spotify General:
# spclient.wg.spotify.com
# ads-fa.spotify.com
# analytics.spotify.com
# audio2.spotify.com
# crashdump.spotify.com
# log.spotify.com
# That should kill off most of Spotify's ads and tracking
# in one swing. Also, this is combined with the ad list
# above so it should also block 3rd party ads as well as
# 1st party ads from Spotify.
#
# I strictly block Spotify ads due to Spotify's lack of
# ability to provide safe, non-malaware/spyware ads that
# don't compromise user security and saftey. If you choose
# to disable these rules, understand your security is severly
# at risk and the posibility for maleware that can easily and
# remotley be triggered is at a reasonable enough level
# that you should consider leaving these rules enabled.

